_sText:
"Well de_tegea_s is on the verge of completion…

This map was originally made for CS 1.6 by a mapper named “3D Punk”.
My friends and I were big fans of the map
and after trying to contact the mapper with no luck, I chose to rebuild the map myself for CS Source with a few additions
which I felt made the maps game play a bit more even.

The map is completed.
Latest updates to the map to make it final.

1. The NPC characters have been removed to improve on frame rates
as well as fix nav mesh issues.
2. Clipped some rocks in one stairwell to avoid players from
getting stuck.
3. Added some new lighting to the map mainly in two dark areas that
would have been camper's paradise.
4. Added nav file for bot play
5. Added working soundscape
6. All files are embedded and fully working."
